parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood latch can cause the hood to fly open while the vehicle is in motion, obstructing the driver's vision and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The hood opens suddenly while driving
the hood does not stay closed
and the wind gets inside the door and causes it to open.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood can cause it to fly open while driving, obstructing the driver's visibility, and potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The hood comes open or flies off while driving

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door hinges can cause the door to hang loose or detach from the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door screws pull through the frame body
the door hangs loose or detaches from the vehicle
the door is only held by a single hinge or bolt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt to lock properly or the buckle to hold in place can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be adequately restrained.
symptoms: The seatbelt locks up too tight and will not loosen
the seatbelt fails to lock in place during an accident
the seatbelt buckle does not hold in place
the buckle can be easily pulled out of place
the seatbelt does not restrain the occupant properly.
